&GLOBAL
  PRINT_LEVEL MEDIUM
  PROJECT dat_Si
  RUN_TYPE DEBUG
&END GLOBAL

&DEBUG
  DEBUG_FORCES T
  DEBUG_STRESS_TENSOR F
  DX 0.0001
  MAX_RELATIVE_ERROR 0.5
&END DEBUG

&FORCE_EVAL
